These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: iced-tea, juice, fanta, sprite
Pet: rat, ferret, pony, bird
1. Pet:bird is on the left of Beverage:fanta##1
2. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left of Pet:ferret##1
3. Beverage:sprite is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:pony is on the left or right of Pet:bird##3
5. Beverage:iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | juice | sprite | fanta |
| Pet        | rat | ferret   | bird | pony    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: time-travel, romance, mystery, western
Nationality: turkish, australian, polish, brazilian
1. Movie-Genre:romance is on the left of Movie-Genre:western##1
2. Nationality:turkish is on the left of Nationality:polish##1
3. Nationality:polish is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:turkish == Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
5. Nationality:australian is on the right of Nationality:polish##1
6. Nationality:turkish == Movie-Genre:time-travel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | time-travel  | romance  | western |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | turkish | polish | australian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: eggplant, mango, cabbage, apricot
Movie-Genre: zombie, adventure, sports, satire
1. Food:apricot is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:satire##3
2. Food:cabbage is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:satire is on the left or right of Food:mango##3
4. Movie-Genre:satire is on the right of Movie-Genre:sports##1
5. Movie-Genre:zombie is in an odd position##4
6. Food:mango is on the right of Food:cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | apricot | cabbage | mango    | eggplant      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports        | satire     | zombie | adventure |

