.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: puzzles, magic-tricks, singing, sudoku
Music-Genre: jazz, r&b, punk, electronic
1. Hobby:magic-tricks is between Music-Genre:jazz and Music-Genre:electronic##2
2. Hobby:sudoku is on the left of Hobby:puzzles##1
3. Music-Genre:punk is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:r&b is on the left of Music-Genre:electronic##1
5. Music-Genre:r&b is on the right of Hobby:puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | sudoku | puzzles | magic-tricks | singing |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | jazz   | r&b    | electronic  |

