2. Music-Genre:punk is on the right of Beverage:mirinda##1
3. Music-Genre:pop is between Music-Genre:punk and Beverage:7up##2
4. Beverage:mirinda is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:pop is on the left or right of Music-Genre:punk##3
6. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Music-Genre:metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate       | 7up   | mirinda | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | techno | metal | pop        | punk    |

